fill each cells: buffer of 4 i32 with value: i32 does:
  for each index i of cells:
    cells at i becomes value

sum buffer each cells: buffer of 4 i32 gives i32:
  let total be 0
  for each index i of cells:
    total becomes total plus cells at i
  total

main gives i32:
  let cells be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0
  fill each cells with 6
  sum buffer each cells
